Mustang Two Four<br><br>
Once again you show the wisdom of your ancestors.  I hope Doc understands the conviction of purpose and the respect for the individual you possess.  You light the path for us to follow.<br><br>
It is easy to continue this journey when we can see the way.  The strong must pervail when there are those who would prey on the weak in time of need.  I am sure your ancestors were aware of those who would dim the light and have us lose our way.  I know they smile upon your example as do I.<br><br>
Doc must understand that even the patience of the strongest can be tested beyond the limit.<br><br>
A Warrior chooses his battles well.
